            <p class="text-base text-body leading-[1.8] m-0">Free Remove BG is a free online background remover that erases the background from any picture in seconds. Powered by AI, it lets you remove bg from image files of every kind, no sign-up, no watermark, and no cost. Whether you need a transparent cutout for a product listing, a profile picture, a logo, or a design mockup, just drop in a photo and let the AI bg remove the background for you. Because the tool is free, unlimited, and works right in your browser, it is a faster, more private alternative to the usual remove bg online services.</p>
